      "rationale": "Three meshes (4.2 M, 9.8 M, and 21.6 M hexahedral cells) were generated with a refinement ratio of 1.52. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI values of 3.1% and 2.4% for the fine-to-medium and medium-to-coarse pairs respectively, both below the 5% threshold. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
