      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions for the Morrison et al. (2022) pulsatile experiments were documented in the test report. Inlet waveform frequency matched the CPB target of 60 bpm ±2 bpm; hematocrit was 33% ±1%; temperature was 37°C ±0.5°C. All parameters within the ±5% tolerance. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
