      "rationale": "Predicted RH values were compared against Morrison et al. (2022) measurements at all five flow-speed combinations. Normalised RMSE was 8.3%, within the 10% acceptance criterion. Individual point errors ranged from 2.1% to 11.7%; the single exceedance at the highest-speed operating point was attributed to measurement uncertainty and accepted by the team. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
