      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory metric for blood pump hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance and ISO 10993-4. The CFD model outputs volume-averaged scalar stress accumulation converted to RH via the Giersiepen–Wurzinger power-law correlation. The QoI is directly traceable to the clinical endpoint of red blood cell damage. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
